raceComments: {"comment":"5. A DIVA is making up for lost time with 2 wins from 4 starts in her initial prep as a 5-year-old. SISTER SHAY franked her Wodonga win with an all-the-way victory at Bendigo nearly 3 weeks ago. She rises 2kg in weight, but the hat-trick beckons. 8. YACHIYO set the pace but offered little at Flemington nearly 5 weeks ago. She might not be ready to race beyond a mile just yet, and can make amends with a dip in class here. Stick with her. 6. COCO JEN has yet to put in a bad performance in 5 starts.
